&lt;li&gt;Multi-terminal management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offline/online sync capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Barcode scanning integration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer display support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manager override functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
